{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"79fcf58f-517b-40d6-a65d-f2e76702536f","content":"No workflow files found in the current directory, so here's general guidance for the switch:\n\n### Changes needed for NuGet Trusted Publishing (OIDC)\n\n**1. Configure NuGet.org** — Register your GitHub repo as a trusted publisher at [nuget.org/manage](https://www.nuget.org/manage) → your package → Trusted Publishers. You'll provide your GitHub org/user, repo name, workflow filename, and optionally an environment name.\n\n**2. Update your workflow:**\n\n```yaml\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    # Required for OIDC token\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write\n      contents: read\n    # Optional but recommended: tie to a GitHub environment\n    environment: nuget-publish\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      # ... build & pack steps ...\n\n      - name: Install .NET\n        uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n\n      # Authenticate via OIDC — no API key needed\n      - name: Authenticate with NuGet\n        run: dotnet nuget update source nuget.org --configfile nuget.config --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n\n      - name: Push\n        run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n        # No --api-key flag needed!\n```\n\n### Key differences from your current setup\n\n| Before (API key) | After (OIDC) |\n|---|---|\n| `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` | No secret needed |\n| `--api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}` | Remove `--api-key` flag |\n| No `permissions` block needed | Add `permissions: id-token: write` |\n| No NuGet.org trusted publisher config | Register repo on NuGet.org |\n\n**3. Remove** the `NUGET_API_KEY` repository secret once everything works.\n\n> **Note:** NuGet trusted publishing is still relatively new. Verify the latest setup steps in the [NuGet docs](https://learn.microsoft.com/nuget/nuget-org/trusted-publishers) as the exact workflow integration may evolve.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"b0a464a8-114a-4c4d-9e92-3c6ba0c7bd28","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"There are no workflow files in the current directory. The user might be asking a general question about how to switch from NuGet API key-based publishing to OIDC-based trusted publishing. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":602,"requestId":"1C1A:A96C7:5C6755F:63E68B5:69FBE326"},"id":"580f8ed1-b2d6-4110-801a-a19c836f2e6a","timestamp":"2026-05-07T00:56:19.305Z","parentId":"f17d8234-ba2f-4889-92bd-f3f4801ef647"}
